{"type": "article", "id": 4895, "title": "Menu 香槟刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-04T08:35:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233417RgV8hFC0BUrH2TPI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t丹麦家居设计品牌 Menu 邀请美国工业设计界的明星 Karim Rashid 为其带来了一款香槟刀新作。每逢聚会，开启香槟的时刻都格外热闹，这一次 Karim Rashid 想让你开香槟的动作更酷一点。这把香槟刀采用不锈钢材质制成，整个外表银光四射，每一把皆是单独打磨而成，挥刀间即可打开香槟，软木塞被斩落，香槟喷薄而出，确保没有玻璃碎片进入瓶内。定价 149.95 美元（约合人民币 930 元），<a href=\"http://store.menudesignshop.com/menu-champagne-sabre-by-karim-rashid-p149.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODYzMzk1MzI0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233416YPdWeZlhUF2p8Qaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233417b4NwsF9CDHc32eQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}